---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Baseball Gear & Tracking Devices | Baseballab"
  description="Rapsodo, FlightScope, swing trackers and more — the best data measurement devices for modern baseball analytics explained."
  ogUrl="https://baseballab.com/en/gear/"
>
  <style slot="head">
    .gear-hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy-dark) 0%, var(--navy) 60%);
      color: var(--white);
      padding: 3.5rem 1.25rem 2.75rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .gear-eyebrow {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(192,57,43,.85);
      font-size: .75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: .3rem .9rem;
      border-radius: 9999px;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .gear-hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.7rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -.03em;
      margin-bottom: .75rem;
    }
    .gear-sub {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.8);
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      font-size: clamp(.9rem, 1.8vw, 1rem);
      line-height: 1.75;
    }
    .breadcrumb { padding: .75rem 0; font-size: .8rem; color: var(--gray-500); }
    .breadcrumb a { color: var(--gray-500); }
    .breadcrumb span { margin: 0 .4rem; }
    .section { padding: 3rem 0 4rem; }
    .gear-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .gear-card {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.6rem 1.4rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: .65rem;
    }
    .gear-icon { font-size: 2rem; line-height: 1; }
    .gear-title { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); }
    .gear-desc { font-size: .88rem; color: var(--gray-600); line-height: 1.65; flex: 1; }
    .gear-link {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .3rem;
      color: var(--red);
      font-size: .84rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .gear-link:hover { gap: .55rem; }
  </style>

  <section class="gear-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="gear-eyebrow">⚙️ Baseball Gear</p>
      <h1>Baseball Gear & Tracking Devices</h1>
      <p class="gear-sub">The measurement devices powering the Statcast era — pitch tracking, swing analysis, and ballistic measurement tools explained.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container">
    <nav class="breadcrumb">
      <a href="/en/">Home</a><span>›</span><span>Gear</span>
    </nav>
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
      "@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"BreadcrumbList",
      "itemListElement":[
        {"@type":"ListItem","position":1,"name":"Baseballab","item":"https://baseballab.com/"},
        {"@type":"ListItem","position":2,"name":"Gear","item":"https://baseballab.com/en/gear/"}
      ]
    })} />
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="gear-grid">
        <div class="gear-card">
          <div class="gear-icon">📡</div>
          <div class="gear-title">Rapsodo</div>
          <p class="gear-desc">Real-time pitch and batting data measurement. Tracks velocity, spin rate, break, exit velocity, and launch angle. Widely used from amateur leagues to professional teams.</p>
          <a href="https://www.amazon.co.jp/s?k=%E3%83%A9%E3%83%97%E3%82%BD%E3%83%BC%E3%83%89+MLM2+PRO&tag=baseballab22-22" class="gear-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer sponsored">View on Amazon →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="gear-card">
          <div class="gear-icon">📊</div>
          <div class="gear-title">FlightScope</div>
          <p class="gear-desc">Doppler radar-based ballistic tracker. High-precision measurement of exit velocity, pitch trajectory, and spin. Used by MLB organizations worldwide.</p>
          <a href="https://www.amazon.co.jp/s?k=FlightScope+%E5%BC%BE%E9%81%93%E8%A8%88%E6%B8%AC+%E9%87%8E%E7%90%83&tag=baseballab22-22" class="gear-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer sponsored">View on Amazon →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="gear-card">
          <div class="gear-icon">⌚</div>
          <div class="gear-title">Swing Tracker</div>
          <p class="gear-desc">Bat-mounted sensor measuring swing speed, path, and impact location. Syncs with a smartphone app to accumulate and analyze swing data over time.</p>
          <a href="https://www.amazon.co.jp/s?k=%E3%82%B9%E3%82%A4%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B0%E3%83%88%E3%83%AC%E3%83%BC%E3%83%8A%E3%83%BC+%E9%87%8E%E7%90%83+%E3%82%BB%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B5%E3%83%BC&tag=baseballab22-22" class="gear-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer sponsored">View on Amazon →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="gear-card">
          <div class="gear-icon">🎥</div>
          <div class="gear-title">High-Speed Camera</div>
          <p class="gear-desc">Slow-motion video capture for grip mechanics, bat path, and ball contact analysis. Widely used for pitching and hitting instruction. Smartphone-compatible models available.</p>
          <a href="https://www.amazon.co.jp/s?k=%E9%AB%98%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6%E3%82%AB%E3%83%A1%E3%83%A9+%E3%82%B9%E3%83%9D%E3%83%BC%E3%83%84+%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90&tag=baseballab22-22" class="gear-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer sponsored">View on Amazon →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
